result.longName: Beijing Deep Glint Technology Co., Ltd.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Beijing DeepGlint Technology Limited develops an artificial intelligence-based computer vision, data intelligence, and temperature measurement application software. The company offers data intelligence platform, which integrates intelligent data access, intelligent data analysis, intelligent data governance, data security output and related capabilities to provide a one-stop for software developers/integrators; dual-light temperature measurement intelligent recognition system, which offers real-time statistics, high temperature alarm, security identification record, infrared imaging preview, custom area monitoring, and personalized data retrieval services; and big data analysis, and smart hardware solutions. It serves security, retail, and finance sectors; transportation hubs, such as railway stations, airports, and subway stations; and densely-populated places, such as government agency, supermarkets, shopping malls, parks, office buildings, campuses, communities, and surrounding villages. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Beijing, China.
